<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">This was an excellent post. Probably shouldn't be in the Rants area seeing as a lot of people avoid it in here. With Gnarls permission I'd like to move it to General.
<br />

<br />
Interesting thoughts on the major games I have to say. I keep hope that sooner or later a game will hit that "mark" for me. I haven't tried WoW yet (hope to soon) and of course Vanguard is on the horizon. EQ2 has come pretty damn close to being an ideal game for my playstyle. 
<br />

<br />
Overall, I'd say that at least from the EQ &lt;-&gt; EQ2 comparison you were right on the money Gnarl. Will be interesting to see what others think about the direction game mechanics are taking.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
